<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3708858>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12. Allodynerus reduncus sp. nov., 1, 3, 5–9, holotype, ♀; 4, 10–12, paratype, ♂. 1–2. Habitus, dorsal view; 3–4. Clypeus, frontal view; 5. Metasoma, dorsal view; 6. Metasoma, ventral view; 7. Propodeum, dorsal views; 8. Vertex and anterior surface of pronotum, dorsal view; 9. Mesosoma, lateral view; 10. Antennal segment, ventral view; 11. Genitalia, ventral view; 12. Penile valve, ventral view. lvv, ventral lobe of penile valve. ap, basal apodeme of penile valve. pb, basal plate of penile valve." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3708858/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3708860>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–19. Allodynerus bimaculus sp. nov., holotype, ♀. 13. Habitus, dorsal view; 14. Clypeus, frontal view; 15. Vertex and anterior surface of pronotum, dorsal view; 16. Metasoma, dorsal view; 17. Propodeum, dorsal view; 18. Metasoma, ventral view; 19. Mesosoma, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3708860/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3708862>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–26. Allodynerus diqingensis sp. nov., holotype, ♀. 20. Habitus, dorsal view; 21. Clypeus, frontal view; 22. Vertex and anterior surface of pronotum, dorsal view; 23. Metasoma, dorsal view; 24. Propodeum, dorsal view; 25. Metasoma, ventral view; 26. Mesosoma, lateral view." ;
