<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3708864>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27–36. Allodynerus asperipunctarus sp. nov., holotype, ♂. 27. Habitus, dorsal view; 28. Clypeus, frontal view; 29. Vertex and anterior surface of pronotum, dorsal view; 30. Antennal segment ventral view; 31. Mesosoma, lateral view; 32. Propodeum, dorsal view; 33. Metasoma, dorsal view; 34. Metasoma, ventral view; 35. Genitalia, ventral view; 36. Penile valve, ventral view. lvv, ventral lobe of penile valve. ap, basal apodeme of penile valve. pb, basal plate of penile valve." ;
